{
  "texts": [
    "The health of crops depends on the prompt diagnosis of plant diseases (Singh and Yogi, 2023).",
    "In this investigation (Singh and Yogi, 2023), CNNs are used to apply DL to automate the diagnosis of diseases in potato leaves.",
    "The paper uses a dataset of 1700 images of potato leaves (600 for training and 300 for testing) to showcase the utility of CNNs in disease identification in intelligent farming.",
    "The citrus potato diseases are considered to be classified.",
    "The CNN model outperforms all other models in accuracy tests, reaching an impressive 99.62% (Table 9)."
  ]
}